OL,3,CTyre fire couple forced to sell home
OL,4,Cin Spain
OL,6,FA couple who were sentenced after a
OL,7,Fhuge fire at their illegal tyre
OL,8,Fstorage site have been ordered to sell
OL,9,Ftheir Spanish home.
OL,11,FIn June 2024, Stuart and Vicky Bedford
OL,12,Fwere sentenced for a number of charges
OL,13,Frelating to two facilities in Bradford
OL,14,Fand Doncaster after being arrested in
OL,15,FSpain.
OL,17,FIt came after a large blaze in
OL,18,FNovember 2020 at the Bradford site,
OL,19,Fwhich saw 100 firefighters deployed
OL,20,Fand caused travel disruption when
OL,21,Froads were closed and trains disrupted.
