OL,6,FBedford, of Fairfax Avenue, Harrogate,
OL,7,Fwas sentenced to 12 months in prison,
OL,8,Fwith Vicky Bedford, of Fairgrey Close,
OL,9,FRipon, was given a 12-month community
OL,10,Forder.
OL,12,FA proceeds of crime hearing on
OL,13,FThursday heard their company
OL,14,FEqualityre had made #1.85m, according
OL,15,Fto the Local Democracy Reporting
OL,16,FService.
