OL,3,CTyre fire couple forced to sell home
OL,4,Cin Spain
OL,6,FEnvironment Agency prosecutor Joseph
OL,7,FMillington told Bradford Crown Court:
OL,8,F"This is how much they earned from
OL,9,Fbringing tyres on the site and the
OL,10,Fcosts avoided from not disposing of
OL,11,Fthem legally."
OL,13,FThe court heard the couple personally
OL,14,Fmade almost #350,000.
OL,16,FThe value of their Spanish property
OL,17,Fwas E80,000 (approximately #70,000),
OL,18,Fthe court was told. The Bedfords were
OL,19,Fordered to sell the home.
