OL,3,CTyre fire couple forced to sell home
OL,4,Cin Spain
OL,6,FMohammed Yaqoob, who owned the site in
OL,7,FBradford, had lost around #89,000
OL,8,Fclearing the site.
OL,10,FMr Millington said: "Mr Yaqoob
OL,11,Fimpressed on me the dramatic impact
OL,12,Fthis has had on his life, his finances
OL,13,Fand his wellbeing and the health of
OL,14,Fhis family.
OL,16,F"It is important victims of crime have
OL,17,Fa voice in this court."
