OL,6,FAnother Bradford business, called
OL,7,FLicensed Tyre Disposals, is yet to be
OL,8,Fsentenced after sending tyres to the
OL,9,Fillegal site at Spring Mill Street.
OL,11,FMr Millington said: "The business was
OL,12,Finvolved in criminality in a different
OL,13,Fway. Licensed Tyre Disposals recently
OL,14,Fhad a change in directorship, and
OL,15,Fthere has been difficulty in
OL,16,Fcontacting the new director."
OL,18,FThe next hearing will take place on 23
OL,19,FJanuary.
